<i>one week before Rosh Hashana</i>

36:48.509 --> 36:51.644
<i>so that you have this moment</i>

36:51.646 --> 36:55.447
and that sound to remind you

36:55.449 --> 36:59.151
that you are not alone.

37:08.863 --> 37:11.797
Alright, everyone.
