39:40.114 --> 39:42.514
It's a well-organized force.
If you want to join them..

39:42.516 --> 39:46.252
Oh, no, I, I don't fight, okay?
I think, therefore I am.

39:46.254 --> 39:49.255
We've been thinking
for 5000 years.

39:49.257 --> 39:53.125
Maybe it's time
to try something else.

39:53.127 --> 39:55.460
Do you really think I could
help anyone with a gun?

39:55.462 --> 39:57.397
Of course not.

40:00.501 --> 40:02.467
Okay.

40:02.469 --> 40:04.803
Look at this, Emma.

40:04.805 --> 40:06.941
Marcel Marceau.

40:13.681 --> 40:16.817
- It's perfect.
