46:19.046 --> 46:20.649
Elsbeth is strong.

46:23.017 --> 46:24.785
Yes, yes.

46:30.090 --> 46:32.560
- Okay. Listen.
- Yeah.

46:34.128 --> 46:37.429
The, uh, the Resistance group
in Lyon.

46:37.431 --> 46:40.733
- What?
- How could we join them?

46:40.735 --> 46:42.200
Who?

46:42.202 --> 46:43.969
What do you mean who?
Me. Us.

46:43.971 --> 46:46.106
- You?
- Yes. Me.

46:47.107 --> 46:48.409
What happened?

46:49.877 --> 46:53.045
We just got stopped by these
Vichy officers

46:53.047 --> 46:56.848
you know, and... I, I just..

46:56.850 --> 46:59.484
I don't want to keep,
like, running, you know

46:59.486 --> 47:01.556
without doing something
about it.

47:04.358 --> 47:08.393
Listen... these Lyon fighters,
they're serious

47:08.395 --> 47:11.396
tough folks,
risking their lives for France.

47:11.398 --> 47:13.633
They get approached by
infiltrators on a regular basis

47:13.635 --> 47:15.568
and if I make contact,
there's no turning back.

47:15.570 --> 47:17.869
- I know.
- If you're just mad because you got stopped.

47:17.871 --> 47:19.438
No, I'm not just mad.

47:19.440 --> 47:23.277
No, I'm... I'm ready to fight.

47:26.347 --> 47:27.680
Georges is expecting more
children.

47:27.682 --> 47:29.682
Yeah, well, Georges
