49:34.475 --> 49:35.976
Did you like it?

49:37.879 --> 49:39.446
You can sing.

49:43.283 --> 49:46.686
That's what
I always wanted to do

49:46.688 --> 49:49.891
but my father was a butcher,
his father was a butcher.

49:52.493 --> 49:55.160
I couldn't just become a singer.

49:55.162 --> 49:56.896
And now you can.

49:56.898 --> 49:58.031
Yes.

49:59.399 --> 50:01.301
Because now I have nothing.

50:02.604 --> 50:05.339
They took everything
but my voice.

50:07.542 --> 50:10.979
So, so wh... why did you
fight my passion?

50:18.653 --> 50:20.855
Because I didn't want you
to starve.

50:22.189 --> 50:25.560
Because most artists cannot make
a living, you know?

50:28.061 --> 50:30.732
At least a butcher
will never be hungry.

50:42.944 --> 50:45.745
That was,
that was a great performance.

50:45.747 --> 50:48.446
- So, you liked it?
- I did like it. I... I..

50:48.448 --> 50:50.983
- Yes?
