50:57.090 --> 50:58.456
and then, you know,
we would feel it.

50:58.458 --> 50:59.692
Okay, I tell you something.

50:59.694 --> 51:03.094
Maybe, when the,
when the war is over..

51:03.096 --> 51:04.664
Mm.

51:04.666 --> 51:06.433
...we, we could..

51:07.835 --> 51:09.837
...we can perform together.

51:12.472 --> 51:16.410
Alain and I are joining
the Resistance.

51:22.850 --> 51:24.684
May Hashem protect you both.

52:56.110 --> 52:58.079
No, no, no.
