Your passports are impressive.

57:42.763 --> 57:46.165
Thank you, sir..
Madam.

57:46.167 --> 57:48.734
Sir is fine, if it helps you.

57:48.736 --> 57:51.236
We're about to receive 20
fighters from Britain.

57:51.238 --> 57:54.073
