Alain. Alain?

1:06:01.863 --> 1:06:03.061
What happened?

1:06:03.063 --> 1:06:05.330
The Gestapo.

1:06:05.332 --> 1:06:06.868
They took everyone.

1:08:09.356 --> 1:08:12.525
Emma and Mila.

1:08:12.527 --> 1:08:13.960
Two Jewish sisters caught

1:08:13.962 --> 1:08:16.096
fighting with
the French Resistance.

1:08:19.834 --> 1:08:23.571
This can end right now if you
tell me where are the men.

1:08:28.208 --> 1:08:29.544
Mm.

1:08:31.045 --> 1:08:33.581
Mila, you stay here.

1:08:36.884 --> 1:08:40.352
Mila. Shh, shh.

1:08:40.354 --> 1:08:43.423
Right there. Don't move!

1:08:45.425 --> 1:08:48.128
Where are you taking her?

