Are you familiar
with the word flaying?

1:09:38.746 --> 1:09:41.582
<i>Also known colloquially
as skinning.</i>

1:09:45.252 --> 1:09:46.219
No?

1:09:47.855 --> 1:09:51.423
<i>It is a method of a slow
and painful execution</i>

1:09:51.425 --> 1:09:53.859
<i>in which the skin
is removed from the body</i>

1:09:53.861 --> 1:09:56.030
while the person
is still alive.

1:09:58.198 --> 1:10:02.668
An attempt is made to keep the
removed portion of skin intact

1:10:02.670 --> 1:10:04.770
<i>and to keep
the person conscious</i>

1:10:04.772 --> 1:10:08.206
<i>for the majority
of the procedure.</i>

