What difference does it make?

1:10:12.013 --> 1:10:13.815
No, Emma.

1:10:17.085 --> 1:10:19.787
I've decided
I'm not going to kill you.

1:10:24.826 --> 1:10:29.063
I'm going to do that to your
sister... in front of you.

1:10:37.105 --> 1:10:38.271
Why?

1:10:41.109 --> 1:10:44.810
Because you don't want to
tell me where the men are.

1:10:44.812 --> 1:10:47.012
If I can't capture them

1:10:47.014 --> 1:10:49.048
I at least want you
to go back to them

1:10:49.050 --> 1:10:51.217
and tell them
what you've endured.

1:10:51.219 --> 1:10:54.754
To see if they want to continue
with their pointless Resistance.

1:10:54.756 --> 1:10:56.055
I don't know where they are.

1:10:56.057 --> 1:10:58.423
- <i>I don't know!</i>
- Ugh.

1:10:58.425 --> 1:11:00.492
I swear.

1:11:00.494 --> 1:11:02.563
I don't believe that.

1:11:09.604 --> 1:11:11.072
Emma?

1:11:13.007 --> 1:11:15.007
<i>What did you do to her?</i>

1:11:15.009 --> 1:11:17.375
I didn't,
I didn't even touch her.

1:11:17.377 --> 1:11:19.580
He wants to know where they are.

1:11:21.048 --> 1:11:22.915
Don't tell him.

1:11:22.917 --> 1:11:24.583
He will kill us all the same!

1:11:24.585 --> 1:11:25.851
So, you do know!

1:11:25.853 --> 1:11:27.520
- I don't.
- <i>You do know!</i>

1:11:27.522 --> 1:11:29.054
- I don't!
- You do know!

1:11:29.056 --> 1:11:31.157
- I don't. I don't!
- <i>Kill me. I don't care.</i>

1:11:31.159 --> 1:11:35.393
We won't be traitors.
