They are children.
I'm an educator.

1:29:11.919 --> 1:29:14.722
What good does it do
to teach them fear?

1:29:53.794 --> 1:29:56.128
- Come with me.
- Huh?

1:29:56.130 --> 1:29:58.132
<i>I said come with me.</i>

1:30:23.456 --> 1:30:24.959
<i>Spread your legs!</i>

1:30:32.867 --> 1:30:34.600
<i>Show me your pockets.</i>

1:30:34.602 --> 1:30:36.137
Show me your pockets.

1:30:38.940 --> 1:30:42.076
It's just a spoon
and here's money.

1:30:45.546 --> 1:30:46.514
What's this?

1:30:47.480 --> 1:30:49.581
