1:31:44.739 --> 1:31:47.573
How do you think

1:31:47.575 --> 1:31:50.911
I can help make sure she becomes
interested in the arts?

1:31:55.316 --> 1:31:56.851
How old is she?

1:31:58.986 --> 1:32:02.388
She is just a baby.

1:32:02.390 --> 1:32:04.456
I'm not talking about
what to do immediately.

1:32:04.458 --> 1:32:05.891
Hm.

1:32:05.893 --> 1:32:09.964
But as a strategy to build her
personality for the future.

1:32:18.706 --> 1:32:21.042
Try not to impose it.

1:32:22.943 --> 1:32:26.614
The more that you impose it..

1:32:28.182 --> 1:32:30.584
...I think, the more she will
rebel against it.

1:32:32.086 --> 1:32:34.219
Let her find her passion.

1:32:34.221 --> 1:32:36.121
Stay out of her way,
you know, if anything

1:32:36.123 --> 1:32:37.790
push her in the opposite
direction.

1:32:37.792 --> 1:32:39.526
Tell her arts are,
are for the weak

1:32:39.528 --> 1:32:41.862
and she'll want to
prove you wrong.

1:33:01.550 --> 1:33:03.150
That's very interesting.

1:33:05.786 --> 1:33:07.655
Very interesting.

1:33:10.958 --> 1:33:12.426
Thank you.

1:33:14.762 --> 1:33:15.930
Go.

1:33:16.565 --> 1:33:18.065
Now.

