Let's take a break over there.

1:38:42.956 --> 1:38:44.559
Okay.

1:39:28.736 --> 1:39:30.101
Okay?

1:39:30.103 --> 1:39:31.606
Thank you.

1:39:40.047 --> 1:39:41.716
You are amazing.

1:39:46.019 --> 1:39:47.421
It's because of you.

1:39:48.523 --> 1:39:50.923
What does that mean?

1:39:58.933 --> 1:40:02.002
When we met, you were only
interested in yourself.

1:40:07.842 --> 1:40:10.208
I'm still only
interested in myself.

1:40:23.257 --> 1:40:24.826
Put it out.

1:40:27.695 --> 1:40:29.094
- <i>Shhh.</i>
- <i>Come on.</i>

1:40:33.501 --> 1:40:34.901
Okay. Everybody to the trees!

1:40:34.903 --> 1:40:36.201
- Leave the bags.
- Leave the bags.

1:40:36.203 --> 1:40:37.404
Leave the bags.

1:40:38.006 --> 1:40:38.905
Let's go.

1:40:38.907 --> 1:40:40.806
- Come!
- Come on, let's move.

1:40:40.808 --> 1:40:42.342
Come on.
Let's move. Go, go!

