- Go!
- No!

1:40:47.047 --> 1:40:48.948
- Are you okay?
- Hurry!

1:40:48.950 --> 1:40:50.816
Come on. Come on, quick.

1:40:56.189 --> 1:40:57.957
Okay, let's go, up to the trees!

1:40:57.959 --> 1:40:59.725
Up! Hurry up. Up.

