- Yes.
- Bring them up!

1:47:42.964 --> 1:47:44.196
They can see her.

1:47:44.198 --> 1:47:45.463
Emma!

1:47:45.465 --> 1:47:47.032
Where's Emma?

1:47:47.034 --> 1:47:49.003
- Over there! Over there!
- Oh!

1:47:51.872 --> 1:47:53.040
Emma!

1:48:04.518 --> 1:48:05.918
- Sit here.
- Emma!

1:48:05.920 --> 1:48:08.554
Emma! Emma! Emma!

1:48:08.556 --> 1:48:09.922
Emma! Emma!

